s in Thailand: Towards an understanding of Wat Phra Dhammakaya and Santi Asoke|url=http://www.ahandfulofleaves.org/documents/New%20Buddhist%20Movements%20In%20Thailand_Mackenzie.pdf|year=2007|location=Abingdon|publisher=[[Routledge]]|isbn=978-0-203-96646-4}}\n*{{Citation|date=10 January 1999|url=http://www.matichonelibrary.com|ref={{harvid|Matichon, 10 January 1999}}|work=Matichon|language=th|accessdate=5 December 2016|script-title=th:\u0e2a\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e28\u0e34\u0e29\u0e22\u0e4c\u0e40\u0e2d\u0e01\u0e18\u0e31\u0e21\u0e21\u0e0a\u0e42\u0e22\u0e42\u0e15\u0e49\u0e02\u0e2d\u0e01\u0e25\u0e48\u0e32\u0e27\u0e2b\u0e32\u0e27\u0e31\u0e14\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e30\u0e18\u0e23\u0e23\u0e21\u0e01\u0e32\u0e22|trans-title=Two of Dhammajayo's main students respond to accusations Wat Phra Dhammakaya|via=Matichon E-library|url-access=subscription}}\n* {{Citation|last=McCargo|first=Duncan|title=The Changing Politics of Thailand's Buddhist Order|year=2012|author-link=Duncan McCargo|journal=Critical Asian Studies|volume=44|issue=4|pages=627\u2013642|publisher=[[Routledge]]|doi=10.1080/14672715.2012.738544|issn=1467-2715}}\n* {{Citation|last=McDaniel|first=Justin|title=Buddhists in Modern Southeast Asia|year=2010|journal=Religion Compass|volume=4|issue=11|pages=657\u2013668|publisher=[[Blackwell Publishing]]|doi=10.1111/j.1749-8171.2010.00247.x}}\n* {{Citation|title=\u0e2a\u0e21\u0e28\u0e31\u0e01\u0e14\u0e34\u0e4c\u0e41\u0e04\u0e49\u0e19\u0e16\u0e39\u0e01\u0e1f\u0e49\u0e2d\u0e07 \u0e02\u0e39\u0e48\u0e25\u0e38\u0e22\u0e18\u0e23\u0e23\u0e21\u0e01\u0e32\u0e22|date=8 December 1999|url=http://www.matichonelibrary.com|ref={{harvid|Naew Na, 8 December 1999}}|work=Naew Na|language=th|accessdate=19 December 2016|trans-title=Somsak angered about being sued, threatens to deal with Dhammakaya|via=Matichon E-library|url-access=subscription}}\n* {{Citation|title=Monks, meditation and missing links: continuity, \"orthodoxy\" and the vijja dhammakaya in Thai Buddhism|date=1 April 2008|url=http://ethos.bl.uk/Or